# Abhikarta LLM - Universal LLM Abstraction Framework

**The Most Comprehensive LLM Abstraction Layer**

[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-2.4.0-blue.svg)](https://github.com/ajsinha/abhikarta)
[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8%2B-brightgreen.svg)](https://www.python.org/)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Providers](https://img.shields.io/badge/providers-11-orange.svg)](#supported-providers)

**One interface. Multiple LLMs. Zero vendor lock-in.**

---

## 🚀 What is Abhikarta LLM?

Abhikarta LLM is a production-ready abstraction framework that provides a **unified interface** to work with **11 different LLM providers** through a single, consistent API. Switch between OpenAI, Claude, Llama, or any other LLM without changing your code.

### Key Highlights

- 🎯 **11 LLM Providers** - From cloud giants to local models
- ⚡ **Ultra-Fast** - Groq provider delivers 500+ tokens/second
- 💰 **Cost-Effective** - Use Ollama for free local inference
- 🔒 **Privacy-First** - GDPR-compliant options with Mistral
- 🛠️ **Feature-Rich** - 36+ features including RAG, function calling, streaming
- 📚 **Well-Documented** - 100+ pages of guides and examples
- 🎓 **Easy to Learn** - 13 comprehensive examples included

---

## 📦 Quick Install

```bash
# Install core package
pip install pydantic numpy urllib3

# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/ajsinha/abhikarta-llm.git
cd abhikarta-llm

# Install package
pip install -e .
```

---

## ⚡ Quick Start (30 seconds)

```python
from llm.abstraction.facade import UnifiedLLMFacade

# Configure provider
config = {
    'providers': {
        'openai': {
            'enabled': True,
            'api_key': 'your-api-key',
            'model': 'gpt-3.5-turbo'
        }
    }
}

# Create facade
facade = UnifiedLLMFacade(config)

# Generate response
response = facade.complete("Explain quantum computing simply")
print(response.text)
```

---

## 🌟 Supported Providers (11)

| Provider | Models | Speed | Cost | Best For |
|----------|--------|-------|------|----------|
| **OpenAI** | GPT-3.5, GPT-4 | Medium | $$$ | General purpose |
| **Anthropic** | Claude 3 | Medium | $$$ | Safety & long context |
| **Groq** 🆕 | Mixtral, Llama | ⚡ Ultra | $$ | Real-time apps |
| **Mistral** 🆕 | 4 models | Fast | $$ | European/GDPR |
| **Ollama** 🆕 | Local models | Medium | **FREE** | Privacy & dev |
| **Together** 🆕 | 50+ models | Fast | $$ | Experimentation |
| **Cohere** | Command | Fast | $$ | Multilingual |
| **Google** | Gemini | Medium | $$$ | Multimodal |
| **HuggingFace** | 1000+ | Varies | $ | Community |
| **Replicate** | 100+ | Medium | $$ | Pay-per-use |
| **Mock** | Testing | Fast | **FREE** | Development |

