## 💎 Complete Feature Set (36+)

### Core Features
- ✅ Unified interface for all providers
- ✅ Zero vendor lock-in
- ✅ Async support
- ✅ Response caching
- ✅ History tracking
- ✅ Error handling & retry
- ✅ Rate limiting
- ✅ Performance metrics

### Advanced Features
- ✅ Function calling / Tool use
- ✅ RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation)
- ✅ Prompt templates
- ✅ Response validation (Pydantic)
- ✅ Batch processing (10-15x faster)
- ✅ Conversation management
- ✅ Embeddings support
- ✅ Semantic caching

### Streaming
- ✅ Real-time token streaming
- ✅ TTFT/TPS metrics
- ✅ Event callbacks
- ✅ Stream buffering

### Security
- ✅ PII detection (12 types)
- ✅ Content filtering (12 categories)
- ✅ RBAC (27 permissions)
- ✅ Audit logging

