## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1. Choose Provider

**Free Local**: Ollama
```bash
curl https://ollama.ai/install.sh | sh
ollama pull llama2
```

**Ultra-Fast**: Groq
```bash
pip install groq
export GROQ_API_KEY="your-key"
```

**GDPR**: Mistral
```bash
pip install mistralai
export MISTRAL_API_KEY="your-key"
```

### 2. Run Examples
```bash
python examples/capabilities/01_basic_usage.py
```

